# Project Topic: Comprehensive Analysis of Health Metrics: Duration, Date, Pulse, and Calorie Trends"

# Project Overview: This project focuses on analyzing a dataset containing health-related metrics such as exercise duration, dates, pulse, and calorie consumption. The primary objectives are to clean and preprocess the data, address missing values, ensure accurate data formatting, and perform exploratory analysis to derive insights into the dataset. The results aim to enable better understanding and preparation of the data for downstream tasks like predictive modeling or reporting.

